headline: Here's How Many Shares of Starbucks Stock You Should Own to Get $1,000 in Yearly Dividends
summary: If you're looking to collect $1,000 per year in dividend income from Starbucks (NASDAQ: SBUX), do you need a tall, grande, or venti number of shares?  The coffee giant, recently sporting a market value of $92.6 billion, was trading at about $81.50 per share as of April 18, 2025.  It was also paying $0.61 per share quarterly in dividends, or $2.44 per share each year.
